Titolo: Hysteria Project 2

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Hysteria Project 2 is a 2011 FMV survival horror adventure game developed and published by French studio BulkyPix for iOS and first released on the App Store on January 27, 2011. It was released as a PlayStation mini available for play on the PlayStation 3 and PlayStation Portable on August 10, 2011, in Europe and August 23, 2011, in North America. The port was published by Sanuk Games. The game is a sequel to the 2009 game Hysteria Project.

